        <description>&lt;img src="https://ignatmaldive.github.io/portfolio/p/teletouch/tele-touch.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Teletouch" /&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;description&#34;&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TeleTouch represents a qualitative advance in telepresence technologies, allowing team members to collaborate in an intuitive and personal way.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TeleTouch facilitates remote collaboration and teamwork without the need for expensive travel, saving time and money while reducing CO2 emissions and your impact on the environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The main advantages of the TeleTouch system are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actual size and eye contact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Calibrated surfaces&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shared workspace&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multi-touch&lt;/li&gt;
